  "message": "fix: correct headless VPS auth instructions (no browser opens)\n\n- launch-onboarding: Fix \"A browser window will open\" \u2192 explain URL copy flow\n- status-check: Fix \"opens a browser window\" \u2192 consistent with headless auth section\n- generate-ssh-key: Add key verification section and complete fingerprint art\n\nUsers on a headless VPS won't have a browser open automatically - they need\nto copy the URL displayed in terminal and open it on their laptop's browser.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
